# Project explanation and how it work

This is a project allowing people to create their own Dokkan Battle card and share them.

## How it work

By login and using the form card on the home page and enter every needed informations, user can create a card.
After creating a card user will be redirected in the newest created card ID page, and will be able to share, modify, or delete it.

## Functionnalities

- Login with Google
- Create / update / delete a card
- Logout
- Share a card

## Architecture

- The project follow the Feature Sliced Design architecture ´see skill for more details´.
- Angular v20 is used, and use Firebase for storing data and authenticate user. Also, a Node/Express API is used for manage emails and images (artwork).
